The design originates from Royal Grotesk light by Ferdinand Theinhardt who also supplied the regular, medium and bold weights. Throughout the years, Berthold has expanded this extremely popular and versatile family. AG Super was developed in 1968 by Guenter Gerhard Lange and is an excellent choice for headlines. In 2001, Guenter Gerhard Lange added more weights for Berthold including Super Italic and Extra Bold italic.
